# НИЦ «Эколог» — brand authority

## Rule priority (strict)

1. `design-system/MASTER.md`
2. `design-system/pages/<page>.md` when building a named page
3. `readme.md`, `tokens/`, `styles.css`
4. `NIC Ecolog - Главная v2.dc.html` — interactive reference
5. `.cursor/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/` — UX patterns, a11y, anti-patterns only. **Never replace brand colors, fonts, or Russian B2B tone.**

## Non-negotiables

- Language: Russian, Cyrillic
- No emoji
- Voice: precise, scientific, peer B2B — no greenwashing hype
- Lead differentiators: «Аналитик Лаб» + project portfolio
- Use CSS custom properties from `tokens/` — avoid hardcoded hex in new code

## Workflow before completing UI tasks

1. Read `design-system/MASTER.md` (+ page override if exists)
2. For UX questions, use ui-ux-pro-max skill or `search.py`
3. Run `design-system/CHECKLIST.md` before marking done
